{"tid":1759294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實勇武，是你，和我","createTime":"2019-11-27T14:26:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T17:50:03.000Z","uid":167634,"like":64,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"cae06e2d2004ec517bc90c553bbcbb3909b9ea66","tid":1759294,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:26:08.000Z","msg":"社運走到現在這階段，大家已是千瘡百孔，不管是勇武還是和理非，對嗎？<br />\n但勇武永遠是這次社運必不可少的元素，你認同嗎？<br />\n勇武到底為香港背負著多少？不是因為他們願作無名英雄；不是因為他們願為香港犧牲，而是他們承擔著大多數香港人所承受不到的受傷、被捕、48小時、罪名、所謂的破壞與犯罪、甚至面對死亡的怯懦。我們不要嘗試為自己的怯懦所辯解，因為有怯懦的想法是正常的，但我們假如為自己的怯懦所辯護，你已不是我們的同路人。勇武是為我們的怯懦，而走上街頭，沒有勇武，就沒有現在的香港！<br />\n<br />\n所以，在勇武休息之時，我們要用盡我們所有的方法，延續這場運動，不知道需要多少時間，一個星期？一個月？半年？一年？希望大家裝備自己的思想，不要勇武再承受我們的怯懦，巨大的，辛苦的，但我們是時候面對自己！<br />\n<br />\n與勇武一同前行，兄弟爬山，齊上齊落！光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">勇武，是你，和我，是每一個人！<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z74dHC1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ74dHC1.jpg&h=0ebf8d1d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be16daf67fcbdbd46439a3e4a66c1dbd12d345e3","tid":1759294,"uid":168941,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:27:35.000Z","msg":"多謝勇武 無同我地割#he"},{"pid":"9a503ff00efca20e979fc7019b17fce2a8cfe7b2","tid":1759294,"uid":264871,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:28:20.000Z","msg":"Be water既精粹其實係可和可勇，香港人never die"},{"pid":"202fd01f87fad778b19ebef03e592719813ae1d6","tid":1759294,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:28:33.000Z","msg":"香港人呢個和勇互補抗爭模式，真係前所未有，而且成功！其實外國人都好欣賞我地，我地應該要繼續堅持，唔好睇少自己"},{"pid":"eccf157e7f26ab28292a3c547242f4584c6f7eeb","tid":1759294,"uid":167634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:29:46.000Z","msg":"只要你有過呢份怯懦，其實你都係勇武，面對佢，當有一日你會自己承擔返！"},{"pid":"e6b6eed952d52bb7a94d29b4bece9b19ccc6208b","tid":1759294,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:30:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c85891fe5d7bb5ea66de622aba14f367d31d8934","tid":1759294,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:31:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5f48960221a7249b8da92633c53cf493519fbc7","tid":1759294,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:32:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68dca5b4912e036b6834472a6c4c87c184865191","tid":1759294,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:32:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1a28af64b4481f79b038415ffa16535e98c2ea4","tid":1759294,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:32:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba88d89a8e74343cbb3273da82325063c22e6e53","tid":1759294,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:33:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"634727c89171fd9e3510b846908b878afc3814aa","tid":1759294,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:33:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a59248e9441401ed694c4fe25f69c7be52e5693","tid":1759294,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:36:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4eff44e9458207c957723d6f13e4a8a72a8453f1","tid":1759294,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:37:18.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"5b8ef391350a486d799c0a24421ae88d08c6aad7","tid":1759294,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:37:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c74ede933d69b381467f8cb99946c87c3c3e879","tid":1759294,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:41:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b1735aaad3eb033039e7b5e88a5f60ca3104a54","tid":1759294,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:43:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cad866aab9a418ba5bba64276c619574c34303e7","tid":1759294,"uid":167634,"li